channel.title: Impression 614 - released
channel.description:
[center][CENTER][IMG]http://impression614.com/logotransp.png[/img] [hr] Rune Error Problem? Fix it here :D
1. Go to your client 2. Look for ''cache614'' 3. Copy it and paste it in your C:/ drive 4. Then rename your cache614 to ''cache'' 5. Run the server -.-
Or another way is You do the same thing with the cache, you copy the cache to c drive then you go to cacheconstans.java and change [CODE] public final static String PATH = "C:/cache/runescape/"; [/CODE] to [CODE] public final static String PATH = "C:/cache614/runescape/"; [/CODE]
done. And now tell me was it soooooo hard? like cant you even read the error? [/CENTER]
[hr]
[B]How To Change IP In Client 1) Go To launch.java CTRL+F Look For 127.0.0.1 2) Go To Applet_Sub1.java CTRL+F Look For 127.0.0.1 3) Save Both 4) Compile 5) Run Server[/B]
[hr]
[B]Why Am I Releasing[/B] I have be getting messages on skype asking when my server will be online again, It will not be online again so i figered I
should release this source and help the community out by giving a 614 With Shops, Etc theres not many out there so here you go.
Enjoy.

[hr]
[COLOR=green][B]Features[/B] Some features: - Home At The Grand Exchange ;) - Workign Teleblock with timer - Working Trading without item duplication - Working Dicing With Custom zone - Working Potion system/eating system - Perfect combat (No overpowered items) - 100% Antiflood - 75% Working friendlist - NO NULLPOINTERS! Stable source - Working bonuses - Super Donator/Premium Donator/Legit Dicer - Working leeches - No dupes - 6 Different PK spots - 3 Multi zones - Usefull commands - Blood/Miasmic barrage - Working Ring of Vigour - Working divine affects - Help Zone With Notafication To Staff When Somone Teles - Loyalty Titles - ::item id amount (Must have tokens to spawn certin items) - Shops . Edit in data/shops/shopname.txt (Not completed)[/COLOR]
